      "value": "<p>At 15th level, you always have an album to resort to when times get tough. Once per full rest, you may spend 5 Vice Points to cast one Silverhand Hijutsu as a full turn action, at no cost. The jutsu must have \"Live Stage\" in the name. When you do this, all creatures reroll initiative, with your allies rolling at advantage and your haters (enemies) at disadvantage.</p>",
